--- CS6650 HW2 Local Ignore Configuration ---

--- 1. Privacy & Security (Keys and Secret Variables) ---

Ignore all key files

*.pem
YumengZeng-cs6650-hw1b.pem

Ignore Terraform variable files (contains sensitive info like your personal IP)

Essential to ignore these to prevent exposing your IP address on GitHub

*.tfvars
terraform.tfvars

Also ignore variable files in JSON format

*.tfvars.json

--- 2. Terraform Related (Prevents massive plugin uploads) ---

Ignore binary plugin directory created by terraform init

.terraform/

Recursively ignore any .terraform directory that might appear

**/.terraform/

Ignore state records generated by Terraform runs

*.tfstate
*.tfstate.backup

Ignore dependency lock file

.terraform.lock.hcl

--- 3. Go Compilation & Docker Related ---

Ignore binary files generated by running go build locally

godocker
go-docker-demo

--- 4. OS-Specific Junk ---

.DS_Store

Recommended to include if you have ever operated on Windows:

Thumbs.db

--- 5. Notes ---

Note: This file only protects content within the hw2 folder